---
title: Sweet Chilli Salmon Noodle Bowl with Stir-Fried Veg and Sesame Seeds
description: Salmon is a delicate and flavoursome fish, perfect for absorbing flavours such as the sweet chilli sauce in this recipe. Paired with sticky hoisin-teriyaki noodles loaded with veg, it's a real catch!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R46_W41_UK_R23294-3_MAIN_low_2-3b915c4e.jpg
